  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>研究估计全美患有柠檬黄过敏症的总人数约为360,000，约占总人口的0.12％。<ref>Elhkim, M. O., & ''et al.'' (2006). "New considerations regarding the risk assessment on Tartrazine: An update toxicological assessment, intolerance reactions and maximum theoretical daily intake in France". ''Requl. Toxicol. Pharmacol.'', 47(3), 308-316.</ref>

